Bakasura - Food Ordering Website
This repository contains the code for a responsive food ordering website where users can browse through a variety of dishes, add items to their cart, place orders, and make payments. The website is designed to provide users a seamless online food ordering experience, allowing restaurant owners to manage orders efficiently.
About the Project

The Food Ordering Website allows customers to:
•	Browse and search for dishes from a menu.
•	Add items to their cart and place an order.
•	Select delivery complete payments online.

Restaurant owners can manage:
•	Menu items, including adding, updating, and deleting dishes.

Features
•	User Authentication: Sign up, login
•	Menu Browsing: Customers can browse food items categorized by cuisines or meal types.
•	Cart System: Add or remove items to/from the cart, view total prices.
•	Order Placement: Customers can place orders for delivery or pickup.

Technologies Used
•	Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
•	Others: Bootstrap
